{"tid":2379710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【佐敦封區】被迫停業商戶要求每戶賠2萬元 張建宗昨稱無計劃冀體諒 區議員批「冷血、涼薄」","createTime":"2021-01-25T11:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T12:12:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e085130550c7c2ee523718d40a1aad10d71a691d","tid":2379710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"政府圍封佐敦「受限區域」兩天，今日（25日）凌晨解封，區內過百家商戶期間被迫停業。商戶今日要求政府向每戶提供一筆過2萬元的現金補償，賠償封區兩天的損失，但政務司司長張建宗昨日表示政府沒計劃賠償並「希望大家體諒」。<br />\n<br />\n協助商戶的油尖旺區議會副主席余德寶批評張的說法「冷血、涼薄」，有區內商戶反問：「張生（張建宗）話希望市民體諒吓，但你有無體諒過我哋呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37523/%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-37525/%E3%80%90%E4%BD%90%E6%95%A6%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%AF%8F%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%A02%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E6%98%A8%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%86%80%E9%AB%94%E8%AB%92-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%89%B9%E3%80%8C%E5%86%B7%E8%A1%80%E3%80%81%E6%B6%BC%E8%96%84%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F37523%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-37525%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%25A02%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2598%25A8%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%2586%2580%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%25AB%2592-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2589%25B9%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2586%25B7%25E8%25A1%2580%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%25B6%25BC%25E8%2596%2584%25E3%2580%258D&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABZgFNMR